{"tid":1386870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人原來善忘到上星期5 七警案上訴成功,去到今日仲可以講睇埋聽日先知法治死左未","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:26:43.000Z","uid":47905,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"df8611d62c6a399015a7195acb5414af3d940b92","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:09:40.000Z","msg":"7隻狗2隻唔洗坐 5隻減刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時隔一星期都冇<br />\n全香港人可以唔記得晒 然後走去講睇下聽日點判先知香港仲有冇法治<br />\n<br />\n真心好撚攰<br />\n屌極都仲係咁多ON9,仲以為香港有法治<br />\n<br />\n仲係度諗義士坐完監之後點樣安排工作比佢地<br />\n我屌撚晒你地訓醒未呀<br />\n救所有義士唯一方法係推返呢個政府<br />\n唔係幫佢地搵工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每位手足走出黎既目的就係推返極權政府<br />\n有雙普選,還政於民<br />\n你地就繼續諗要比呢個政權統治多一百年<br />\n我真係唔知點樣先可以屌醒你地<br />\n香港就快玩完,仲係掛住每日返工<br />\n<br />\n只有一個方法可以救到義士<br />\n就係推返極權政府<br />\n唔該,所以香港人要有呢個覺悟,唔好覺得行上街政府就會理你<br />\n依家無左呢支歌仔唱<br />\n大家一日無呢個覺悟,一日做唔到全城勇武<br />\n基本上無可能贏,不如投降算<br />\n<br />\n醒啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6469174998738ac208e543da4c4a20af81670f","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe35e964ed26dda303ba7eefc8f21740782e6d15","tid":1386870,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:13:02.000Z","msg":"8.5全民罷工 今次到我哋和理非主場 唔好比個垃圾港共政權睇死我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f131fb146c56f542b1a4fe4b0bbfc3e21a5a600e","tid":1386870,"uid":108902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:13:50.000Z","msg":"8.5全民罷工 今次到我哋和理非主場 唔好比個垃圾港共政權睇死我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推上熱門"},{"pid":"ad44704ead3a9a4d263a302365be3bf24b6baf8f","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308f4fd43dc5d64c7fc6b02c2dbf390ad07cffe4","tid":1386870,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"［文宣唔該］罷工冇人理？屌港豬之餘，唔該望下工聯會騎劫左幾多個工會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1384172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1384172</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d366b0e18124042f46b4c8ec45bb98305d033648","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c79fdf8d4c116c9919fa6106b950eadd9a9c5eb","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4f467c817c45648dbe74b72e51513af0f44b04","tid":1386870,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:27:54.000Z","msg":"各位我地依家得最後呢條路 陪審團否決權<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386844\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386844</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b1fb7a8619257ba4289d26d95d7d6ac5e583184f","tid":1386870,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:30:51.000Z","msg":"又唔可以咁講，因為星期六日都有行動，推左先都冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番香港獨立呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n2047到時只會都係變返中國，仲要一下子就變，一定好多人接受唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭"},{"pid":"b52a4e44e5676ab42cdbbb00ef55372599ccad81","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ed5872ccc5bc99bee2a2c66acbb8e806cc2483","tid":1386870,"uid":59225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49704e75a3e4d5cd3446f68e8fa3f21b12957fbe","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fda64734b3270f5bcaa12eb273e37951dd11f9","tid":1386870,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"